sub_title: Technology Program Analyst at TE Connectivity
summary:
An International Relations & Foreign Trade professional with experience working in the Chamber of Commerce of Gijón and the Port Authority of Gijón. Studies in Innovation Management. Fluent in Spanish, English and French. Accustomed to working in a team and meeting deadlines. 

Seeking new professional opportunities.
